{"id": 2130, "genre": 1001, "title": "多年谍战片的熏陶，你都看烦了哪些老套路数？", "description": "在众多 bug 里扒拉出一点不那么出戏的亮点，就堪称口碑剧了。（题图来自：pixabay）", "record_count": 2612, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180118103447rnUvELcuXhNyRC49.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-18T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 260097, "content": "谍战剧只服柳云龙", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047562}, {"id": 262156, "content": "主角总是在一阵惊心动魄的音乐中啥事没有。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1142064}, {"id": 261646, "content": "枪打在主角身上，就是打不死，总能救回来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245143}, {"id": 260624, "content": "中文无人不晓，全都会说", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1087593}, {"id": 262673, "content": "中国人的优秀", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776389}, {"id": 260625, "content": "掏枪之时还不忘剧情发展（爱情）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1087593}, {"id": 266006, "content": "每次救人的时候都互相让对方先走，结果两个都没走成。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1267211}, {"id": 260120, "content": "好人总是赢", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1241539}, {"id": 283937, "content": "Bond~ James Bond   老哥，你都说了50年了。你是个职业间谍啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1356971}, {"id": 260650, "content": "誓死保卫情报的时候明明寡不敌众 主角光环不会死", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097424}, {"id": 260395, "content": "难道谍战剧不是两党地下工作者大型相亲现场吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923997}, {"id": 260652, "content": "打仗什么的不要紧，重要的是跟美女谈情说爱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1242876}, {"id": 261679, "content": "一把手枪可以打死一群敌人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246053}, {"id": 260656, "content": "孤独和烈酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1242057}, {"id": 260657, "content": "啊西巴，孤独寂寞，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1242057}, {"id": 262707, "content": "一定会擦出爱的火花", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215719}, {"id": 260671, "content": " 腰部持枪射击", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674056}, {"id": 260928, "content": "主角一定会赢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243814}, {"id": 260674, "content": "敌人总是很愚蠢，这不真实", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1229088}, {"id": 260675, "content": "一看就知道好人坏人，概念化！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1229088}, {"id": 260933, "content": "反派总是有大小喽啰衬托反派的蠢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678859}, {"id": 259922, "content": "主人公都是计划通，从不出纰漏", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 259923, "content": "主角有失误也多半是设计好的陷阱，看得一点都不紧张，安详坐等反转", "image": null, "praise_count": 153, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 259924, "content": "开头各种小细节突出接头的巧妙，一有什么事都是街头大声交谈，没在怕的", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 261204, "content": "建议大家看看《风筝》?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829863}, {"id": 259925, "content": "新中国成立即结束，地下工作者的努力都得到了回报", "image": null, "praise_count": 356, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 260439, "content": "男主角的发型大多是现代才流行的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1241855}, {"id": 260695, "content": "反派老是说，这次我们已经做好了准备，万无一失", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243206}, {"id": 264537, "content": "智能子弹自动绕主角，自动打鬼子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1259266}, {"id": 259929, "content": "反派死的莫名其妙，智商总被主角吊打", "image": null, "praise_count": 156, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1121412}, {"id": 259930, "content": "这一part 难道不是“神预测”的台词嘛！什么 8年抗战就要开始了，25000里的长征在路上......balabala的", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240619}, {"id": 259931, "content": "没咋看过?", "image": null, "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966594}, {"id": 262237, "content": "不仅谍战片，好多剧里，演员都不会关门，或没关上，或没关严。这应该不是谍战片里的套路。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1248333}, {"id": 259933, "content": "剧情推进到一半，在危难时候发现某个领导是自己人", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037652}, {"id": 259934, "content": "辣眼睛不敢看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212802}, {"id": 259935, "content": "主角的行动不管多么惊险，哪怕反派马上进门，也不会被拆穿抓住", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066005}, {"id": 259938, "content": "打鬼子就像是，茶余饭后的娱乐活动。", "image": null, "praise_count": 267, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107047}, {"id": 259939, "content": "不管啥片，谈情说爱最重要。", "image": null, "praise_count": 247, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205342}, {"id": 259940, "content": "女特务审讯共产党员", "image": null, "praise_count": 57, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022071}, {"id": 259941, "content": "正派人物临死前总要啰嗦几句，反派人物直接死", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255265}, {"id": 260709, "content": "都是装逼666的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964570}, {"id": 259942, "content": "执行任务前想象任务完成后的生活，这种人基本死在任务中", "image": null, "praise_count": 216, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255265}, {"id": 259943, "content": "360度无死角 主角光环异常强大", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235585}, {"id": 259944, "content": "总有你以为的好人不是好人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240782}, {"id": 259945, "content": "子弹是打不中主角的", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660957}, {"id": 259946, "content": "主角爱上的人一定跟自己不是一个党派或者不是一个阵营", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240787}, {"id": 259947, "content": "在办公室偷文件，外面脚步声传来，啪，门一开，镜头一转，里面空无一人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 401, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 405835}, {"id": 259948, "content": "总是成功", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835482}, {"id": 259949, "content": "大部分主角都是看过剧本的，沉着得一批。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205949}, {"id": 259950, "content": "不管正面人物是怎么死的，少不了那一抹嘴角的血。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240803}]}